> Linas Vepstas wrote:
>> The current driver code performs 512 DMA mappns of a bunch of 
>> 32-byte structures. This is silly, as they are all in contiguous 
>> memory. Ths patch changes the code to DMA map the entie area
>> with just one call.
>> 
